defaultIn order to create an evidence-based management plan for Lyme Bay, the project has put in place significant scientific studies. These will inform the level of fishing effort and other measures required to sustainably manage the fisheries and maintain a balanced ecosystem. Examples of these studies are:
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;defaultProject next stepsdefaultBLUE is now planning to lead the project through the next stage to ensure a properly planned, well-managed, scientifically-backed, and sustainable fishery. 
defaultThis project will: 
