default2)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAre all IFCAs and other regulators open to such public/private partnership arrangements?  Some are less so than others.
default3)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAre there ways of achieving new MPAs with multiple benefits through this way of working?
